ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
Immigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectCanada-British Columbia Immigration Agreement
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration ENTER INTO the CANADA-BRITISH COLUMBIA IMMIGRATION AGREEMENT with the Government of British Columbia, which provides that the Agreement will be valid for five years from the date on which it is signed by both parties.
